            "title": "差估署 : 1月私樓價格指數連跌兩個月  創8年半低",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">香港差餉物業估價署數據顯示，1月私人住宅售價指數跌至287.6，連跌2個月，創近8年半新低。1月樓價按月跌0.45%，按年跌6.4%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上月中小型單位按月跌0.4%，按年跌6.4%;大型單位按月跌約1%，按年跌5.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">1月私人住宅租金指數連升兩個月，升至192.9，是4個月以來最高，按月升約0.42%，按年升約4%。中小型及大型單位按月都升0.4%以上，按年分別升逾4%及近1.8%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14741659-%e5%b7%ae%e4%bc%b0%e7%bd%b2-1%e6%9c%88%e7%a7%81%e6%a8%93%e5%83%b9%e6%a0%bc%e6%8c%87%e6%95%b8%e9%80%a3%e8%b7%8c%e5%85%a9%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88-%e5%89%b58%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%8a%e4%bd%8e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240726_PP_PROPERTY_INDEX_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-28 16:20:42",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "全日收市︱失守二萬三 恒指挫 點報 點 車股捱沽 比亞迪電子挫逾10%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股午後愈跌愈深，恒生指數相繼失守10天線與二萬三關口，尾市曾跌逾900點，主板成交連續第2日過4000億。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指於昨天上午才一度升越24000點，時隔1日，大市形勢便完全兩樣。在美國關稅威脅，疊加輝達業績勝預期但績後股價仍顯著向下，港股今早借勢下滑。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指數今早低開102點、報23616點，即為大市封頂，半日已挫逾500點，但仍險守10天線(最新約為23134點)，午後則與內地A股齊齊拾級向下，相繼失守10天線及23000點，後段跌幅曾擴大至919點，低見22798點，其後才略為反彈；恒指最後收報22941點，跌776點或3.28%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數跌勢更烈，收挫312點或5.32%，報5568點；國企指數跌317點或3.63%，報8417點。主板成交4062.64億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">不過，2月份單月港股依然錄得可觀升幅，恒指單月累漲2716點或13.43%；科指單月累計升844點或17.88；國指單月累升1035點或14.02%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14741662-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%a4%b1%e5%ae%88%e4%ba%8c%e8%90%ac%e4%b8%89-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e6%8c%ab-%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b1-%e9%bb%9e-%e8%bb%8a%e8%82%a1%e6%8d%b1%e6%b2%bd-%e6%af%94",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-web_HKStock-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-28 16:20:39",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "內地A股午後不斷試底 滬指收挫67點 深指跌2.89% 中芯A股失守百元關",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">面對美國關稅威脅，內地A股全日反覆試底，滬深兩市股指以接近全日低位收市，中芯A股(688981.SH)亦失守百元關口。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_00981-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_00981-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早低開13點後拾級向下，初段最高僅見3383點，仍跌4點，半日已跌29點，午後更愈跌愈深，尾市最多曾跌69點，低見3318點；滬指收報3320點，仍跌67點或1.98%，成交7580.55億元(人民幣‧下同)。單周累計則跌1.72%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指再度跑輸，初段高位僅報10883點，跌43點，其後不斷反覆尋底，最低見10583點，跌343點；深指最後收報10611點，仍挫316點或2.89%，跌幅較中午收市時擴大逾倍，全日成交縮減至1.11萬億元。單周累計跌3.46%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數也跌78點或1.97%，以3890點收市；創業板指數跌86點或3.82%，報2170點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/02/20240222_FI_source-ap_輝達_英偉達_Nvidia-2.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/02/20240222_FI_source-ap_輝達_英偉達_Nvidia-2.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">各主要板塊幾乎全部下挫，輝達(Nvidia)業績勝預期，但績後股價依然顯著向下，內地上市芯片股也捱沽。中芯國際A股跌4.54%，報97.79元；華虹(01347)A股(5688347.SH)跌5.06%，報52.4元；AI芯片概念股寒武紀(688256.SH)更挫7.61%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日前受合併傳聞炒上的中金公司(03908)與中國銀河(06881)，相關A股經前兩日抽升後，今日終明顯回吐。中金A股(601995.SH)收挫9.26%，報35.27元；中國銀河(601881.SH)跌幅亦擴大至收市時跌6.51%，報16.66元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">釀酒行業是少數逆市向好的板塊，但午後板塊內亦有不少股份掉頭倒跌，五糧液(000858.SZ)便跌0.88%，古井貢酒(000596.SZ)也微跌0.02%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：貴州茅台官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240513_FI_source-web_600519-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：貴州茅台官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240513_FI_source-web_600519-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：貴州茅台官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">貴州茅台(600519.SH)則保持強勢，只是升幅難免收窄，收市時升15.23元或1.03%，報1500.79元；皇台酒業(000995.SZ)也升2.39%，酒鬼酒(000799.SZ)升1.23%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14741490-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e4%b8%8d%e6%96%b7%e8%a9%a6%e5%ba%95-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e6%8c%ab67%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c2-89-%e4%b8%ad%e8%8a%afa%e8%82%a1%e5%a4%b1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250206_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-28 15:21:02",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
