            "title": "中港股市午後續尋底 恒指逼近23000點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中港股市午後進一步尋底，恒生指數稍早前有下試23000點之勢。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至下午1時40分，恒指報23078點，跌640點或2.7%，早前最低曾見23016點；恒生科技指數報5619點，跌261點或4.45%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地A股同樣在午後初段反覆向下，深指曾跌逾2%，滬指則跌超過1.2%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14741165-%e4%b8%ad%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%b8%82%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e7%ba%8c%e5%b0%8b%e5%ba%95-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e9%80%bc%e8%bf%9123000%e9%bb%9e",
